  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Professional Profile</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10 text-justify">
    Experienced Civil Engineer with over 8 years of expertise in structural design and urban planning. Specialized in 
    delivering innovative engineering solutions for residential, commercial, and infrastructure projects across Egypt. 
    Proven track record in managing complex projects from concept to completion, ensuring compliance with international 
    building codes and sustainable construction practices. Strong background in both structural analysis and comprehensive 
    urban planning with focus on creating functional, safe, and cost-effective solutions.
